import { Card, Grid, Typography, } from '@material-ui/core'
import ToggleButton from '@material-ui/lab'
import { WbSunnyIcon, NightsStayIcon, } from '@material-ui/icons'

const AvailabilityComponent = () => {
    return (
        <Card>
            <Grid justify="center" direction="column" align="center" container xs={12} spacing={1}>
                <Typography>Availability</Typography>
                <Grid item container justify="space-between" direction="row" item xs={12} spacing={1}>
                    <Typography>Mon</Typography>
                    <Typography>Tue</Typography>
                    <Typography>Wed</Typography>
                    <Typography>Thu</Typography>
                    <Typography>Fri</Typography>
                    <Typography>Sat</Typography>
                    <Typography>Sun</Typography>
                </Grid>
                <Grid>
                    <ToggleButton
                        value="check"
                        selected={selected}
                        onChange={() => {
                            setSelected(!selected);
                        }}
                    >
                        <WbSunnyIcon />
                    </ToggleButton>
                </Grid>
            </Grid>
        </Card>
    )
}

export default AvailabilityComponent
